+    "generatedAt": "2026-02-27"
+  },
+  "lawrence-ooty": {
+    // ... etc
+  }
+}
+```
+
+---
+
+## Ready to Go?
+
+**Default plan:** I'll auto-generate all routes with Mapbox, start implementing Cesium today, and you can refine specific routes as we test.
+
+Sound good? 🚀
